# DDGRO Project Structure Guide

## Frontend (ddgro-form/)
The main Next.js application with internationalization support.

### Key Entry Points
- Main layout: [src/app/layout.tsx](mdc:src/app/layout.tsx)
- Home page: [src/app/page.tsx](mdc:src/app/page.tsx)
- Localized pages: [src/app/[locale]/](mdc:src/app/[locale]/)
- Form components: [src/components/form/](mdc:src/components/form/)

### State Management
- Redux store: [src/store/index.js](mdc:src/store/index.js)
- Form slice: [src/store/slices/formSlice.js](mdc:src/store/slices/formSlice.js)

### Styling
- Global styles: [src/app/globals.css](mdc:src/app/globals.css)
- SCSS components: [src/scss/](mdc:src/scss/)
- Tailwind config: [tailwind.config.js](mdc:tailwind.config.js)

### Internationalization
- Message files: [messages/](mdc:messages/)
- Middleware: [middleware.ts](mdc:middleware.ts)

## Backend (ddgro-nowy-backend/)
Express.js API server with MongoDB integration.

### Key Entry Points
- Main app: [ddgro-nowy-backend/app.js](mdc:ddgro-nowy-backend/app.js)
- Server startup: [ddgro-nowy-backend/bin/www](mdc:ddgro-nowy-backend/bin/www)

### API Routes
- Base routes: [ddgro-nowy-backend/routes/](mdc:ddgro-nowy-backend/routes/)
- API endpoints: [ddgro-nowy-backend/routes/api/](mdc:ddgro-nowy-backend/routes/api/)

### Models & Data
- MongoDB models: [ddgro-nowy-backend/models/](mdc:ddgro-nowy-backend/models/)
- Database migrations: [ddgro-nowy-backend/migrations/](mdc:ddgro-nowy-backend/migrations/)

### Services
- Email service: [ddgro-nowy-backend/services/sendEmail.js](mdc:ddgro-nowy-backend/services/sendEmail.js)
- Authentication: [ddgro-nowy-backend/config/passport.js](mdc:ddgro-nowy-backend/config/passport.js)
